
This folder contains the code for producing the result of method “Spatial_3” in the paper.
The full details about this method can be found in the following article.

Spatial Econometrics , James P. LeSage Department of Economics University of Toledo 

Instruction:

1. Run the “historical_maker.m” to generate the in-control beta (general Spatial Model estimates) and estimated variance.

2. Run the “ARL_out_of_control.m” for each shift scenario
